  "title": "Blockchain for Scaling Climate Action 📈❄️ | Roundup #62",
  "slug": "roundup-62",
  "html": "<hr><p><em>Hey there Regens! </em>🌱<em> <a href=\"https://twitter.com/mayazdentzel\">Maya</a> here, an academic researcher and digital ethnographer of web3 and climate. I'm excited to be back this week to share some exciting news from my working group at <a href=\"https://www.weforum.org/press/2022/09/new-crypto-sustainability-coalition-to-investigate-potential-of-web3-technologies-in-fighting-climate-change/\">WEF Crypto Sustainability Coalition</a> – we have recently published a comprehensive whitepaper on blockchain for scaling climate action </em>🎉<em> So in this week's roundup we will cover a snapshot summary of the publication, and as always, the top news and developments from across the world of Regenerative Finance (ReFi). Let's get into it! </em>🤓</p><hr><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card\"><a href=\"https://www.weforum.org/whitepapers/blockchain-for-scaling-climate-action\"><img src=\"__GHOST_URL__/content/images/2023/04/Screenshot-2023-04-27-at-5.34.22-PM.png\" class=\"kg-image\" alt loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1780\" height=\"1300\" srcset=\"__GHOST_URL__/content/images/size/w600/2023/04/Screenshot-2023-04-27-at-5.34.22-PM.png 600w, __GHOST_URL__/content/images/size/w1000/2023/04/Screenshot-2023-04-27-at-5.34.22-PM.png 1000w, __GHOST_URL__/content/images/size/w1600/2023/04/Screenshot-2023-04-27-at-5.34.22-PM.png 1600w, __GHOST_URL__/content/images/2023/04/Screenshot-2023-04-27-at-5.34.22-PM.png 1780w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 720px) 720px\"></a></figure><h1 id=\"blockchain-for-scaling-climate-action-%F0%9F%A6%8B\">Blockchain for Scaling Climate Action 🦋</h1><p>When most people think of cryptocurrency, they may immediately conjure up images of volatile prices, scams, and questionable use cases. And while it's true that this has played a prominent role in crypto's history, there is more to the story than meets the eye. Beneath the surface is a technology that has the potential to be a game-changer in the fight against climate change and other pressing global issues. </p><p>The key to unlocking this potential is understanding how blockchain and other decentralized technologies can be <u>harnessed in the right way</u> and building the right <u>partnerships</u> to make it happen. But how can we speed this process up? </p><h3 id=\"the-wef-crypto-sustainability-coalition\">The WEF Crypto Sustainability Coalition</h3><p>Made up of over 30+ key partners, The World Economic Forum (WEF) announced the launch of the Crypto Sustainability Coalition in September 2022. The aim has been to investigate how Web3, crypto, and blockchain technologies can be utilised to achieve positive climate action, support research &amp; development, share best practices, and influence positive regulation on climate-related matters.</p><p><em>Check out the <a href=\"https://www.refidao.com/community/working-group/WEF-Crypto-Sustainability-Coalition/r/recAFA1XV8rh6hjDR\">working group dashboard on ReFiDAO.com</a> </em>👇</p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-bookmark-card\"><a class=\"kg-bookmark-container\" href=\"https://www.refidao.com/community/working-group/WEF-Crypto-Sustainability-Coalition/r/recAFA1XV8rh6hjDR\"><div class=\"kg-bookmark-content\"><div class=\"kg-bookmark-title\">WEF Crypto Sustainability Coalition | ReFi Working Group</div><div class=\"kg-bookmark-description\">A cross-sector coalition to investigate how Web3 and blockchain tools can be utilised to achieve positive climate action.</div><div class=\"kg-bookmark-metadata\"><img class=\"kg-bookmark-icon\" src=\"https://softr-prod.imgix.net/applications/315eb8e9-290e-4a79-a55d-826970df6cd7/assets/c616c43f-de22-4ad8-b857-f44f1718f278.png?rnd&#x3D;1678209594579\" alt=\"\"><span class=\"kg-bookmark-author\">ReFi Working Group</span></div></div><div class=\"kg-bookmark-thumbnail\"><img src=\"https://v5.airtableusercontent.com/v1/16/16/1682949600000/Y9LVCde_Zx-x6pm8qhLEdA/2zSlHmrQ4iP3JCj3qMbQOypVFVLBO4SlwN5orBxalJlzNY2iDx_I3yUtrP82Ji2fru-Kko3Frhj1WBdCISJtOFiybtA5EG186SlPQe1LwNE/DzUokiiK5zkA_MyUa2ry9RxHK8OjGXkR1llNR1UW0HY\" alt=\"\"></div></a></figure><p>Now, after 7 months of research, the working group has just published a comprehensive whitepaper on blockchain for scaling climate action. Let's dive in to key findings 👇</p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-embed-card\"><blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\"><p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">Get insights from <a href=\"https://twitter.com/annalerner?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@annalerner</a> &amp; <a href=\"https://twitter.com/michaelmezz?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@michaelmezz</a> of <a href=\"https://twitter.com/clim8collective?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@clim8collective</a>, <a href=\"https://twitter.com/johnx25bd?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@johnx25bd</a> of <a href=\"https://twitter.com/ToucanProtocol?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@ToucanProtocol</a>, and <a href=\"https://twitter.com/e_cheikos?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@e_cheikos</a>, <a href=\"https://twitter.com/Hayley_L_Anna?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@Hayley_L_Anna</a>, <a href=\"https://twitter.com/mayazdentzel?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@mayazdentzel</a> of <a href=\"https://twitter.com/wef?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@wef</a> on how blockchain technology can support meaningful climate action &amp; real-world use cases.<br><br>Read more ↓<a href=\"https://t.co/azdlyNhTL0\">https://t.co/azdlyNhTL0</a></p>&mdash; Celo 🦇 🌳 (@CeloOrg) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/CeloOrg/status/1651663257017413656?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">April 27, 2023</a></blockquote>\n<script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script>\n</figure><h3 id=\"more-funding-less-warming-%F0%9F%92%B0\">More funding, less warming 💰</h3><p>We have interviewed 23 leaders and experts in the ReFi sector and collected over 60 survey responses 📃.  This paper investigates how blockchain is incentivizing a planet-positive economy focused on financing regeneration and climate action at scale. It is particularly urgent as trillions more dollars of climate finance investment are needed to maintain the 1.5°C pathway set by <a href=\"https://www.ipcc.ch/sr15/#:~:text=Limiting%20warming%20to%201.5°C%20implies%20reaching%20net%20zero,particularly%20methane%20(high%20confidence).\">IPCC</a>. </p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card kg-card-hascaption\"><img src=\"__GHOST_URL__/content/images/2023/04/Screenshot-2023-04-29-at-1.18.51-PM.png\" class=\"kg-image\" alt loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1286\" height=\"1038\" srcset=\"__GHOST_URL__/content/images/size/w600/2023/04/Screenshot-2023-04-29-at-1.18.51-PM.png 600w, __GHOST_URL__/content/images/size/w1000/2023/04/Screenshot-2023-04-29-at-1.18.51-PM.png 1000w, __GHOST_URL__/content/images/2023/04/Screenshot-2023-04-29-at-1.18.51-PM.png 1286w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 720px) 720px\"><figcaption><strong>The trillions of dollars needed vs actual flows | <a href=\"https://www.climatepolicyinitiative.org/publication/global-landscape-of-climate-finance-2021/\">Climate Policy Initiative</a></strong></figcaption></figure><h3 id=\"why-blockchain-x-refi-%F0%9F%A7%90\">Why Blockchain X ReFi? 🧐</h3><p>Blockchain can provide the necessary infrastructure to combat climate change at speed and scale. Specifically, the whitepaper identified:</p><ul><li>💪 Blockchain can strengthen trust and ambition in climate negotiations.</li><li>📈 Blockchains and digital Measurement, Reporting, &amp; Verification (MRV) technologies can improve market transparency and credibility.</li><li>💸 Digital carbon markets can funnel more money to project developers.</li><li>🌱 Digitization democratizes access to climate action.</li></ul><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card kg-card-hascaption\"><img src=\"__GHOST_URL__/content/images/2023/04/Screenshot-2023-04-29-at-1.23.21-PM.png\" class=\"kg-image\" alt loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1556\" height=\"553\" srcset=\"__GHOST_URL__/content/images/size/w600/2023/04/Screenshot-2023-04-29-at-1.23.21-PM.png 600w, __GHOST_URL__/content/images/size/w1000/2023/04/Screenshot-2023-04-29-at-1.23.21-PM.png 1000w, __GHOST_URL__/content/images/2023/04/Screenshot-2023-04-29-at-1.23.21-PM.png 1556w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 720px) 720px\"><figcaption><a href=\"https://www.weforum.org/whitepapers/blockchain-for-scaling-climate-action\">WEF</a></figcaption></figure><blockquote>ReFi intersects with climate technology, sustainable development, climate finance, economics, regenerative practices, impact investment and climate justice – to name a few 🌿</blockquote><h3 id=\"industry-trends-%F0%9F%93%8A\">Industry trends  📊</h3><p>The current market development is headed in the right direction, utilizing cutting-edge blockchain technology for climate-focused innovations.</p><ul><li>🌍 Web3 incentives strengthen existing climate initiatives (e.g. <a href=\"https://climateactiondata.org\">Climate Action Data Trust</a>)</li><li>🏢 Companies have a growing focus on climate impact and more ambitious net-zero commitments (e.g. <a href=\"https://consensys.net/blog/press-release/cop27-leading-technology-companies-launch-ethereum-climate-platform-initiative-to-address-ethereums-former-proof-of-work-carbon-emissions/\">Ethereum Climate Platform</a>)</li><li>📡 Emerging digital MRVs unify the market (e.g. renewable energy certificates by <a href=\"https://twitter.com/all_infra\">Allinfra</a>)</li><li>👩🏽‍💻 Data ownership and interoperability are key features of the industry (e.g. <a href=\"https://twitter.com/HYPHEN_AG\">Hyphen</a>)</li><li>🤝 ReFi prioritizes the role of community and collaborative culture (e.g. <a href=\"https://twitter.com/moss_earth\">Moss</a>, <a href=\"https://www.ethichub.com/es/\">EthicHub</a>)</li></ul><figure class=\"kg-card kg-embed-card\"><blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\"><p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">Climate impact orgs 🤝 Global South<br>A recently published <a href=\"https://twitter.com/wef?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@wef</a> paper finds that 15% of companies leveraging blockchains to scale climate action are based or have offices in the Global South<br><br>Read the paper 👇<a href=\"https://t.co/Tr6UBXUWl1\">https://t.co/Tr6UBXUWl1</a></p>&mdash; Toucan (@ToucanProtocol) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/ToucanProtocol/status/1651466317684264966?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">April 27, 2023</a></blockquote>\n<script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script>\n</figure><h3 id=\"the-challenges-%F0%9F%AB%A3\">The challenges 🫣</h3><p>But it's not easy, there are several challenges that we need to tackle to fully maximize blockchain for scaling climate action.</p><ul><li>🚀 Implementation at scale requires unprecedented speed and coordination </li><li>📰 The blockchain industry is facing serious reputational challenges </li><li>👩‍🏫 Complexity and education gaps in the space persist </li><li>🔎 Real-world impact goes before digital engagement </li><li>👩‍⚖️ ReFi suffers from regulatory uncertainty </li></ul><figure class=\"kg-card kg-embed-card\"><blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\"><p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">The World Economic Forum <a href=\"https://twitter.com/wef?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@wef</a> published a white paper titled Blockchain For Scaling Climate Action, where our CEO &amp; Co-Founder Dana Gibber was mentioned when talking about the importance of constructive regulation to enable responsive digital climate innovation at scale.⚖️</p>&mdash; Flowcarbon (@weareflowcarbon) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/weareflowcarbon/status/1650963330465427469?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">April 25, 2023</a></blockquote>\n<script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script>\n</figure><h3 id=\"recommendations-and-whats-next-%F0%9F%94%AE\">Recommendations and what's next 🔮</h3><p>All in all, the speed and scale of adoption will depend on constructive regulation. To get there, the blockchain industry should learn from the evolution of the climate industry, build multi-stakeholder partnerships and focus on scaling responsibly. Developing these partnerships, alongside educational campaigns &amp; effective storytelling, will deepen institutional ties and accelerate progress. </p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card kg-card-hascaption\"><img src=\"__GHOST_URL__/content/images/2023/04/Screenshot-2023-04-29-at-2.04.14-PM.png\" class=\"kg-image\" alt loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1751\" height=\"390\" srcset=\"__GHOST_URL__/content/images/size/w600/2023/04/Screenshot-2023-04-29-at-2.04.14-PM.png 600w, __GHOST_URL__/content/images/size/w1000/2023/04/Screenshot-2023-04-29-at-2.04.14-PM.png 1000w, __GHOST_URL__/content/images/size/w1600/2023/04/Screenshot-2023-04-29-at-2.04.14-PM.png 1600w, __GHOST_URL__/content/images/2023/04/Screenshot-2023-04-29-at-2.04.14-PM.png 1751w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 720px) 720px\"><figcaption>Source: <a href=\"https://www.weforum.org/whitepapers/blockchain-for-scaling-climate-action\">WEF</a></figcaption></figure><p>In summary, ReFi founders, investors, and buidlers need to stay laser-focused on solving real-world problems and providing evidence-based, measurable impact to ensure industry momentum and credibility. Let's level up! 💪</p><div class=\"kg-card kg-button-card kg-align-center\"><a href=\"https://www.weforum.org/whitepapers/blockchain-for-scaling-climate-action\" class=\"kg-btn kg-btn-accent\">Read full white paper</a></div><hr><div class=\"kg-card kg-header-card kg-width-full kg-size-small kg-style-image\" style=\"background-image: url(https://blog.refidao.com/content/images/2023/02/ReFi-Cover-1.png)\" data-kg-background-image=\"https://blog.refidao.com/content/images/2023/02/ReFi-Cover-1.png\"><h2 class=\"kg-header-card-header\" id=\"refi-newsbites-%F0%9F%97%9E%EF%B8%8F\">ReFi NewsBites 🗞️</h2><h3 class=\"kg-header-card-subheader\" id=\"em-stylebox-sizing-border-boxthe-latest-updates-across-refi-twitter-and-beyondem\"><em style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">The latest updates across ReFi Twitter and beyond...</em></h3></div><h2 id=\"refi-dao-is-live-on-gitcoin-%F0%9F%8E%89\">ReFi DAO is live on Gitcoin 🎉</h2><p>We’re on a mission to realize a global regenerative economy rooted in startup cities all around the globe. With this long-term goal, <a href=\"https://twitter.com/refidaoist\">ReFi DAO</a> is supporting the emergence of a network of regenerative villages in strategic startup cities in 2023 with the belief that regeneration begins within 🧘‍♀️</p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-embed-card\"><blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\"><p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">We are LIVE on <a href=\"https://twitter.com/gitcoin?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@gitcoin</a>!<a href=\"https://t.co/5CryTjtlkB\">https://t.co/5CryTjtlkB</a><br><br>We&#39;re on a mission to build a global regenerative economy rooted in startup cities around the world 🌍<br><br>We&#39;re also hosting our first Featured Round supporting local <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/ReFi?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#ReFi</a> economies in 18 cities—primarily in the global south.<br><br> /1 <a href=\"https://t.co/NhVIOL4trm\">pic.twitter.com/NhVIOL4trm</a></p>&mdash; ReFi DAO 🌍 #GitcoinBeta (@refidaoist) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/refidaoist/status/1650873125264056323?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">April 25, 2023</a></blockquote>\n<script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script>\n</figure><p>Thanks for being part of our journey and supporting us along the way 🙏🏼</p><div class=\"kg-card kg-button-card kg-align-center\"><a href=\"https://explorer.gitcoin.co/#/round/1/0xaa40e2e5c8df03d792a52b5458959c320f86ca18/0xaa40e2e5c8df03d792a52b5458959c320f86ca18-243\" class=\"kg-btn kg-btn-accent\">Support here</a></div><h2 id=\"gitcoin-coordination-game-%F0%9F%95%B9%EF%B8%8F\">Gitcoin coordiNATION game 🕹️</h2><p>Together with <a href=\"https://twitter.com/greenpillglobal\">Green Pill</a>, <a href=\"https://twitter.com/regensunite\">Regens Unite</a>, <a href=\"https://metacrisis.xyz/\">Metacrisis.xyz</a>, and others, ReFi DAO is hosting a four-day coordiNATION game rooted in a multitude of cities across the globe. The aim is to onboard new donors, funders, and projects into the <a href=\"https://twitter.com/gitcoin\">Gitcoin</a> ecosystem - for the <a href=\"https://grants.gitcoin.co/\">Beta grants round</a> and beyond 💫  <a href=\"https://www.refidao.com/Gitcoin-CoordiNATION\"><strong>Come get involved</strong></a>!</p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card kg-card-hascaption\"><a href=\"https://www.refidao.com/Gitcoin-CoordiNATION\"><img src=\"__GHOST_URL__/content/images/2023/05/telegram-cloud-photo-size-4-5942736357174656674-y.jpg\" class=\"kg-image\" alt loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1280\" height=\"640\" srcset=\"__GHOST_URL__/content/images/size/w600/2023/05/telegram-cloud-photo-size-4-5942736357174656674-y.jpg 600w, __GHOST_URL__/content/images/size/w1000/2023/05/telegram-cloud-photo-size-4-5942736357174656674-y.jpg 1000w, __GHOST_URL__/content/images/2023/05/telegram-cloud-photo-size-4-5942736357174656674-y.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 720px) 720px\"></a><figcaption><a href=\"https://www.refidao.com/Gitcoin-CoordiNATION\">https://www.refidao.com/Gitcoin-CoordiNATION</a></figcaption></figure><figure class=\"kg-card kg-embed-card\"><iframe width=\"200\" height=\"113\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/hK2RLWmx-rA?feature=oembed\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" allowfullscreen title=\"Gitcoin coordiNATION game is LIVE! 🎉 | Green Pill, Regens Unite, Metacrisis.xyz &amp; ReFi DAO! 🌏🌍🌎\"></iframe></figure><div class=\"kg-card kg-button-card kg-align-center\"><a href=\"https://www.refidao.com/Gitcoin-CoordiNATION\" class=\"kg-btn kg-btn-accent\">Join the game...</a></div><h2 id=\"refi-hippies-nft-collection-has-dropped-%F0%9F%8E%89\">ReFi Hippies NFT collection has dropped<strong> 🎉</strong></h2><p><a href=\"https://twitter.com/loa_labs\">LOA Labs</a> launched the <a href=\"https://medium.com/@LOA_Labs/refi-hippies-a-sustainable-nft-collection-on-stargaze-7e34d50df03e\">ReFi Hippies NFT collection</a> as part of <a href=\"https://twitter.com/regen_network\">Regen Network</a>'s Earth Day drop with the <a href=\"https://twitter.com/StargazeZone\">Stargaze NFT platform</a> 🌍</p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-embed-card\"><blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\"><p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">✌️🏾Snag your <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/ReFiHippie?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#ReFiHippie</a>, now minting!<br><br>Created by <a href=\"https://twitter.com/loa_labs?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@loa_labs</a> and <a href=\"https://twitter.com/BlackArtistFND?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@BlackArtistFND</a> for the <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/EarthDay?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#EarthDay</a> NFT Drop with <a href=\"https://twitter.com/StargazeZone?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@StargazeZone</a> and Regen Network 💫 <a href=\"https://t.co/krFcHboXOc\">https://t.co/krFcHboXOc</a></p>&mdash; Regen Network (@regen_network) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/regen_network/status/1649517119032426496?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">April 21, 2023</a></blockquote>\n<script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script>\n</figure><h2 id=\"refi-at-consensus-%F0%9F%8F%99%EF%B8%8F\">ReFi at Consensus 🏙️</h2><p><a href=\"https://twitter.com/CoinDesk\">CoinDesk</a> brought together a hand-selected mix of DeFi, ReFi, and Institutional participants to sit around tables and discuss how blockchain can accelerate climate action. Regens had a strong presence <a href=\"https://twitter.com/consensus2024\">Consensus 2023</a> with talks by <a href=\"https://twitter.com/dave_fortson\">Dave Fortson</a>, <a href=\"https://twitter.com/filecoingreen\">Filecoin Green</a>, <a href=\"https://twitter.com/regen_network\">Regen Network</a> and <a href=\"https://consensys.net/blog/press-release/cop27-leading-technology-companies-launch-ethereum-climate-platform-initiative-to-address-ethereums-former-proof-of-work-carbon-emissions/\">Ethereum Climate Platform</a> 🌿</p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-embed-card\"><blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\"><p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">LOA’s <a href=\"https://twitter.com/dave_fortson?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@dave_fortson</a> took the stage yesterday with some better world blockchain experts to unpack ESG, climate and blockchain.  🎤🌎 <a href=\"https://t.co/vtMuSYFOHW\">pic.twitter.com/vtMuSYFOHW</a></p>&mdash; LOA LABS (@loa_labs) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/loa_labs/status/1651983376285302784?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">April 28, 2023</a></blockquote>\n<script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script>\n</figure><figure class=\"kg-card kg-embed-card\"><blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\"><p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">“At Regen Network, we fundamentally believe that it’s our moral obligation to build a nature-positive future by 2030.”<br><br>-<a href=\"https://twitter.com/erde_kette?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@erde_kette</a> at <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/Consensus2023?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#Consensus2023</a>, <a href=\"https://twitter.com/CoinDesk?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@CoinDesk</a>’s Projects to Watch <a href=\"https://t.co/5GSUoCODl4\">pic.twitter.com/5GSUoCODl4</a></p>&mdash; Regen Network (@regen_network) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/regen_network/status/1651971960295813120?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">April 28, 2023</a></blockquote>\n<script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script>\n</figure><h2 id=\"refi-regulation-%F0%9F%91%A9%E2%80%8D%E2%9A%96%EF%B8%8F\"><strong>ReFi &amp; Regulation 👩‍⚖️</strong></h2><p><a href=\"https://twitter.com/BL4SG_\">The Blockchain Law for Social Good Center</a> has launched the Earth month celebration by featuring insights on policy and regulation by key thinkers in the ReFi space 💚</p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-embed-card\"><blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\"><p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">📢 More R&amp;R (<a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/ReFi?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#ReFi</a> and <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/regulation?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#regulation</a>) from <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/BL4SG?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#BL4SG</a> Advisory Board Member, Cathy Mulligan <a href=\"https://twitter.com/API_Economics?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@API_Economics</a>! <a href=\"https://t.co/48rtrtn7AL\">pic.twitter.com/48rtrtn7AL</a></p>&mdash; The Blockchain Law for Social Good Center (@BL4SG_) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/BL4SG_/status/1651722839974891520?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">April 27, 2023</a></blockquote>\n<script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script>\n</figure><h2 id=\"also-on-our-radar-this-week\"><strong>Also on our radar this week </strong></h2><ul><li>🇪🇺 The <a href=\"https://www.europarl.europa.eu/news/en/press-room/20230414IPR80133/crypto-assets-green-light-to-new-rules-for-tracing-transfers-in-the-eu\">EU Parliament</a> has voted in favor to pass the <a href=\"https://kpmg.com/de/en/home/insights/2023/04/markets-in-crypto-assets-regulation.html\">MiCA (Markets in Crypto-Assets Regulation)</a> crypto framework.</li><li>🤟 <a href=\"https://twitter.com/ReFiMedellin\">ReFi Medellín</a> becomes a new local node.</li><li><a href=\"https://twitter.com/regen_network\">Regen Network</a> and <a href=\"https://twitter.com/ToucanProtocol\">Toucan </a>launched the <a href=\"https://twitter.com/RuspiTorpi/status/1649380815011213313?t=vuya6G8fyBb3wrb3ulg5TQ&amp;s=19\">Polygon and Cosmos NCT bridge</a></li></ul><hr><h3 id=\"submit-content-ideas-or-feedback-%F0%9F%91%87%F0%9F%8F%BD\">Submit content ideas or feedback 👇🏽</h3><p><em>Want to see a story featured in next weeks Roundup? Or have any feedback? We would love to hear from you!</em></p><div class=\"kg-card kg-button-card kg-align-center\"><a href=\"https://www.refidao.com/content-feedback\" class=\"kg-btn kg-btn-accent\">Submit Feedback</a></div><hr><div class=\"kg-card kg-header-card kg-width-full kg-size-small kg-style-image\" style=\"background-image: url(https://blog.refidao.com/cont