al credits efficient, effective, and scalable.</li></ol><p><strong><strong>Votes have now been reset</strong></strong> so head over to <a href=\"https://www.refidao.com/ecosystem/organizations?ref=blog.refidao.com\">refidao.com</a>, make an account, and show some support to your favourite projects in the ecosystem this week! 💚</p><div class=\"kg-card kg-button-card kg-align-center\"><a href=\"https://www.refidao.com/ecosystem/organizations?ref&#x3D;blog.refidao.com\" class=\"kg-btn kg-btn-accent\">Vote away!</a></div><hr><h3 id=\"add-your-refi-project-%F0%9F%91%87%F0%9F%8F%BD\">Add your ReFi Project! 👇🏽</h3><p><em>Have a project you want to add to our database? Click the button below to submit an application!</em></p><div class=\"kg-card kg-button-card kg-align-center\"><a href=\"https://www.refidao.com/submit-refi-organization\" class=\"kg-btn kg-btn-accent\">Submit project</a></div><hr><div class=\"kg-card kg-header-card kg-width-full kg-size-small kg-style-image\" style=\"background-image: url(https://blog.refidao.com/content/images/2023/01/ReFi-Cover-6.png)\" data-kg-background-image=\"https://blog.refidao.com/content/images/2023/01/ReFi-Cover-6.png\"><h2 class=\"kg-header-card-header\" id=\"refi-podcasts-%F0%9F%8E%99%EF%B8%8F\">ReFi Podcasts 🎙️</h2><h3 class=\"kg-header-card-subheader\" id=\"emtop-audio-and-video-content-from-creators-across-the-web-em%F0%9F%98%8A\"><em>Top audio and video content from creators across the web </em>😊</h3></div><h2 id=\"next-generation-quadratic-funding-with-joel-miller-%F0%9F%92%B0\">Next Generation Quadratic Funding with Joel Miller 💰</h2><p>Tune in to episode #109 of the Green Pill podcast with <a href=\"https://twitter.com/owocki\">Kevin Owocki</a> to learn about <a href=\"https://twitter.com/CS_Synthesist\">Joel Miller</a>'s (PhD candidate at the University of Illinois Chicago) research on pluralistic quadratic funding, collusion resistance, and incentivization across social differences 💻.</p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-embed